You can enable cool mode via the `coolMode` prop on the `RainbowKitProvider`.

```tsx
import { RainbowKitProvider } from '@rainbow-me/rainbowkit';

const App = () => (
  <RainbowKitProvider coolMode {...etc}>
    {/* Your App */}
  </RainbowKitProvider>
);
```

